---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<div class="comps">
		<h1>Design Inspiration</h1>
		<p class="subtitle">Personal websites of farmers, ag leaders, and farmer-entrepreneurs</p>

		<div class="grid">
			<a href="https://johnkempf.com" target="_blank" class="card">
				<h2>John Kempf</h2>
				<p>Amish farmer from Ohio who founded Advancing Eco Agriculture. Working farmer who built a tech/consulting company serving other farmers. Hosts the Regenerative Agriculture Podcast.</p>
			</a>

			<a href="https://chrissacca.com" target="_blank" class="card">
				<h2>Chris Sacca</h2>
				<p>Founder of Lowercarbon Capital, investing heavily in ag-tech and food/agriculture climate solutions. Clean personal branding with strong visual hierarchy.</p>
			</a>

			<a href="https://sarahkmock.com" target="_blank" class="card">
				<h2>Sarah K Mock</h2>
				<p>Agricultural writer and researcher who grew up on a Wyoming farm. Former Farmers Business Network marketing team. Author of <em>Farm (and Other F Words)</em>.</p>
			</a>

			<a href="https://www.thelunaticfarmer.com" target="_blank" class="card">
				<h2>Joel Salatin</h2>
				<p>Multi-generational Virginia farmer, author of 16 books, owner of Polyface Farm. Bridges traditional farming with innovation and thought leadership.</p>
			</a>

			<a href="https://forrestpritchard.com" target="_blank" class="card">
				<h2>Forrest Pritchard</h2>
				<p>Seventh-generation farmer, NYT bestselling author. Converted his family's conventional operation to one of the oldest grass-finished livestock farms in the country.</p>
			</a>

			<a href="https://www.rickbayless.com" target="_blank" class="card">
				<h2>Rick Bayless</h2>
				<p>Fourth-generation food family. James Beard award-winning chef and founder of the Frontera Farmer Foundation supporting Midwestern family farms.</p>
			</a>

			<a href="https://www.tomcolicchio.com" target="_blank" class="card">
				<h2>Tom Colicchio</h2>
				<p>Chef, farmer, and food system advocate. Dual identity as hands-on food producer and national advocate. Strong hero imagery and clean navigation.</p>
			</a>

			<a href="https://www.masumoto.com" target="_blank" class="card">
				<h2>David Mas Masumoto</h2>
				<p>Multi-generational Japanese-American organic peach and grape farmer in California. Author of 15 books. Balances e-commerce with authentic storytelling.</p>
			</a>

			<a href="https://www.farmerd.com" target="_blank" class="card">
				<h2>Daron "Farmer D" Joffe</h2>
				<p>Farmer who built a consulting business serving agriculture. Board member of Heifer International. Pioneer of "agrihoods" integrating farms into communities.</p>
			</a>

			<a href="https://www.apricotlanefarms.com" target="_blank" class="card">
				<h2>John & Molly Chester</h2>
				<p>Transformed 234 depleted acres into a thriving regenerative farm. Featured in <em>The Biggest Little Farm</em>. Beautiful photography and brand design.</p>
			</a>

			<a href="https://brownsranch.us" target="_blank" class="card">
				<h2>Gabe Brown</h2>
				<p>North Dakota rancher, author of <em>Dirt to Soil</em>. Pioneer of regenerative agriculture who became a national thought leader and consultant.</p>
			</a>

			<a href="https://www.mnmillennialfarmer.com" target="_blank" class="card">
				<h2>Zach Johnson</h2>
				<p>Sixth-generation Minnesota farmer with 1M+ YouTube subscribers. Leverages technology and media to build a brand around farming. Bridges traditional and modern.</p>
			</a>

			<a href="https://newforestfarm.us" target="_blank" class="card">
				<h2>Mark Shepard</h2>
				<p>Wisconsin farmer trained in mechanical engineering. Applies systems thinking to agriculture on his 106-acre research farm. Engineer + farmer dual identity.</p>
			</a>

			<a href="https://www.kristinkimball.com" target="_blank" class="card">
				<h2>Kristin Kimball</h2>
				<p>Harvard graduate who left NYC to found a 500-acre diversified farm in upstate New York. Author of <em>The Dirty Life</em> and <em>Good Husbandry</em>.</p>
			</a>

			<a href="https://lisamhamilton.com" target="_blank" class="card">
				<h2>Lisa M. Hamilton</h2>
				<p>Writer and photographer covering agriculture and rural communities for 20+ years. Author of <em>Deeply Rooted</em>. Earth-tone palette with professional typography.</p>
			</a>

			<a href="https://farmerwillallen.com" target="_blank" class="card">
				<h2>Will Allen</h2>
				<p>Milwaukee-based urban farmer, founder of Growing Power, MacArthur "Genius Grant" recipient. Named one of the World's Most Powerful Foodies by Forbes.</p>
			</a>

			<a href="https://www.nickwallaceculinary.com" target="_blank" class="card">
				<h2>Nick Wallace</h2>
				<p>Mississippi chef who grew up on a family farm. Built a business empire rooted in agricultural heritage. Strong farm-roots-to-entrepreneur personal branding.</p>
			</a>

			<a href="https://rajpatel.org" target="_blank" class="card">
				<h2>Raj Patel</h2>
				<p>Food systems author and UT Austin researcher. Systems thinker focused on food and agriculture policy. Clean, minimalist, content-focused personal site.</p>
			</a>

			<a href="https://www.eliotbarbara.com" target="_blank" class="card">
				<h2>Eliot Coleman & Barbara Damrosch</h2>
				<p>Pioneers of four-season organic farming in Maine. Eliot developed new systems and tools for year-round growing, then taught those methods worldwide.</p>
			</a>

			<a href="https://chrissmaje.com" target="_blank" class="card">
				<h2>Chris Smaje</h2>
				<p>Small-scale farmer and former social scientist. Bridges analytical/systems thinking with hands-on farming. Author of <em>A Small Farm Future</em>.</p>
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.comps {
		max-width: 960px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
		font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
		color: #1a1a1a;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
	}

	.subtitle {
		color: #666;
		margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.card {
		display: block;
		padding: 1.25rem;
		border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
		border-radius: 8px;
		text-decoration: none;
		color: inherit;
		transition: border-color 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
	}

	.card:hover {
		border-color: #999;
		box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
	}

	.card h2 {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
	}

	.card p {
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
		color: #555;
		margin: 0;
	}
</style>
